cdata.name: RoBust Defense Token
cdata.desc:
ROMAD is a Blockchain-based antivirus platform.The antivirus was designed tofocus on fighting themalware families instead of its virus strains in order to secure the userdevice.It is distributed free of charge and the user will only pay the service when ROMAD successfully repelled the malware attack. In addition, the Stage I uses the blockchain to store the data about the malware attacks repelled and the Stage II uses the blockchain as a foundation for the passive data exchange that is based on the smart-contracts and zero-knowledge proof.

RoBust Defense Token (RBDT) is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency that powers theROMAD Endpoint Defence platform. It includes the associated license key for the ROMAD antivirus, also the RBDT tokenholders can protect his/her own endpoint, distribute the token manually to the 3rd parties, and/or transfer it to the ROMAD marketplace.
